# projects/

## What goes here
- Active workstreams with defined deliverables and a timeline
- Initiatives that have moved past the idea stage into execution

## What does NOT go here
- Pre-execution concepts without timeline (→ `ideas/`)
- One-off tasks or meetings (→ `meetings/`)

## Primary Home Test
File here if the workstream has both deliverables and a timeline.

## Naming Rule
`project-name.md` (lowercase, hyphenated). Example: `arete-mvp.md`

## Required Sections
- Executive Summary
- Bias Check
- Current State (status, blockers, next milestone)
- Compiled Truth
- Timeline Evidence
